Gracchus wished to be chosen tribune for 132 ΒΩ to complete his reforma but was attacked and killed hya mob of senators headed by P. Scipio. Cicero seems here to approve the action of Scipio, but it is'h'ecause he wishes to take similar action against Catiline.
